  "html": "<h2 class=\"\" id=\"2024-48\">2024-48</h2>\n<p class=\"\">Spent a lot of time reflecting this week on how to improve my life and my current circumstances.</p>\n<h3 class=\"\" id=\"daily-check-in--reflections\">Daily Check-In &#x26; Reflections</h3>\n<ul class=\"list-disc\">\n<li class=\"\"></li>\n<li class=\"\">\n<p class=\"\">Mon 10:11 PM: Played around a bit with Pico-8 and Picotron- explored ways of converting images into Pico-8 sprites, made a little minigame with the help of Claude</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"\">\n<p class=\"\">Tuesday: Worked more on my scrapbook-core script, paid for my GMRS license from the FCC</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"\">\n<p class=\"\">Wed 1:11 PM: Made a new PICO-8 game to practice HAM knowledge <a href=\"https://www.lexaloffle.com/bbs/?tid=145776\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"external-link group inline-flex items-center text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400\">https://www.lexaloffle.com/bbs/?tid=145776</a></p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"\">\n<p class=\"\">Thurs: Thanksgiving</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"\">\n<p class=\"\">Fri: Relaxing, listened to Beacon HAM radio net</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"\">\n<p class=\"\">Sun: Created <a href=\"https://github.com/ejfox/criterion-embedding-viz\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"external-link group inline-flex items-center text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400\">criterion-embedding-viz<svg class=\"inline-block w-4 h-4 ml-1 opacity-50 dark:opacity-75 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity align-text-bottom\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"1em\" height=\"1em\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M12 .297c-6.63 0-12 5.373-12 12c0 5.303 3.438 9.8 8.205 11.385c.6.113.82-.258.82-.577c0-.285-.01-1.04-.015-2.04c-3.338.724-4.042-1.61-4.042-1.61C4.422 18.07 3.633 17.7 3.633 17.7c-1.087-.744.084-.729.084-.729c1.205.084 1.838 1.236 1.838 1.236c1.07 1.835 2.809 1.305 3.495.998c.108-.776.417-1.305.76-1.605c-2.665-.3-5.466-1.332-5.466-5.93c0-1.31.465-2.38 1.235-3.22c-.135-.303-.54-1.523.105-3.176c0 0 1.005-.322 3.3 1.23c.96-.267 1.98-.399 3-.405c1.02.006 2.04.138 3 .405c2.28-1.552 3.285-1.23 3.285-1.23c.645 1.653.24 2.873.12 3.176c.765.84 1.23 1.91 1.23 3.22c0 4.61-2.805 5.625-5.475 5.92c.42.36.81 1.096.81 2.22c0 1.606-.015 2.896-.015 3.286c0 .315.21.69.825.57C20.565 22.092 24 17.592 24 12.297c0-6.627-5.373-12-12-12\" class=\"\"></path></svg></a> to generate embeddings for 4855 movies (9350 texts over 468 batches, using 389,205 tokens from the Nomic embedding API) - will work on visualizing these later</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 class=\"\" id=\"-learning--media\">📚 Learning &#x26; Media</h2>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"https://youtu.be/d8PndpFPL8g?si=s2K8iRI8KwSPGgAg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"external-link group inline-flex items-center text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400\">https://youtu.be/d8PndpFPL8g?si=s2K8iRI8KwSPGgAg</a></p>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/live/J09O0ypZt84?si=3e2QRXNyyCONlBM8\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"external-link group inline-flex items-center text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400\">https://www.youtube.com/live/J09O0ypZt84?si=3e2QRXNyyCONlBM8<svg class=\"inline-block w-4 h-4 ml-1 opacity-50 dark:opacity-75 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity align-text-bottom\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"1em\" height=\"1em\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M23.498 6.186a3.02 3.02 0 0 0-2.122-2.136C19.505 3.545 12 3.545 12 3.545s-7.505 0-9.377.505A3.02 3.02 0 0 0 .502 6.186C0 8.07 0 12 0 12s0 3.93.502 5.814a3.02 3.02 0 0 0 2.122 2.136c1.871.505 9.376.505 9.376.505s7.505 0 9.377-.505a3.02 3.02 0 0 0 2.122-2.136C24 15.93 24 12 24 12s0-3.93-.502-5.814M9.545 15.568V8.432L15.818 12z\" class=\"\"></path></svg></a></p>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"https://youtu.be/KS2AYMyxWAo?si=COWQJcTQiPF2Xr6M\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"external-link group inline-flex items-center text-blue-600 